# ORIG TITLE    More delays at Berlin’s new airport and it’s not even open . 
# ORIG CONTENT  Berlin mayor Klaus Wowereit has stepped down from his post as board chairman of Berlin’s new international airport after technical problems delayed the opening. Berlin Brandenburg was due to open in 2012, but the facility looks set to remain idle until 2014. The cost of the project has doubled to a whopping 4 billion euros. 
